# Changelog

Русская версия: [CHANGELOG.ru.md](CHANGELOG.ru.md)

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/).

## [0.2.0] - 2026-06-21

### Added

- Rolling 24h spend: daily brief now computes spend from total_usage deltas
  over a time-based window, instead of using /auth/key.usage_daily which
  is a calendar-day counter that resets at midnight UTC. This aligns with
  the OpenRouter dashboard's "Past 1 Day" metric.
- `usage_reference` parameter in report builders: /auth/key.usage_daily is
  now shown as a secondary reference line when it differs significantly
  from the primary rolling window value.
- Fallback tests for empty history coverage.

### Changed

- daily_brief main(): rolling history window is now the PRIMARY source of
  truth for 24h spend. Falls back to usage_daily only when history is empty.

### Fixed

- Daily brief now uses a rolling 24-hour delta of total_usage from history
  as the primary source of truth, instead of /auth/key.usage_daily which
  is a calendar-day counter that resets at midnight UTC. This aligns the
  reported spend with the OpenRouter dashboard's "Past 1 Day" metric.